ShowControlPanel: Show Control Panel
AdvancedSearch: Advanced Search
Server:  Server
Filter/Fields/Caption: Field names
Filter/Fields/Description: searches for all field names of all tiddlers in the wiki.
Filter/ContentType/Caption: View the content type.
Filter/ContentType/Description: lists the content types of all entries in the Wiki.
Filter/Languages/Caption: list of languages
Filter/Languages/Description: Lists the installed languages.
Filter/Plugins/Caption: List of plugins.
Filter/Plugins/Description: List of installed plugins.
Filter/Themes/Caption: List of themes.
Filter/Themes/Description: List of installed themes.
Filter/Untagged/Caption: Untagged
Filter/Untagged/Description: lists untagged entries, which can be difficult to find without tags
ActionString/NewTiddlerFromSelectedText/Caption: Create new tiddler
ActionString/NewTiddlerFromSelectedText/Description: Use selected text as the title, selected:
ActionString/NewTiddlerAskTitle/Caption: Create new tiddler (type title)
ActionString/NewTiddlerAskTitle/Description: Enter the create-tiddler wizard and type the title
ActionString/NewTiddlerAskTitle/VariableCaption: Tiddler title
ActionString/NewTiddlerAskTitle/VariableDescription: Enter the title to create
ActionString/AddTags/Caption: Add tags to current tiddler
ActionString/AddTags/Description: Append one or more tags to the current tiddler
ActionString/AddTags/VariableCaption: New tag
ActionString/AddTags/VariableDescription: Type tag name with autocomplete from existing tags
ActionString/CloseTiddler/VariableCaption: Tiddler to Close
ActionString/CloseTiddler/VariableDescription: Leave empty to close current tiddler
ActionString/EditTiddler/VariableDescription: Leave empty to edit current tiddler
ActionString/DeleteTiddler/VariableDescription: Leave empty to delete current tiddler
ActionString/CloneTiddler/VariableDescription: Leave empty to clone current tiddler